The paper deals with optimization problems related to set packing and 3-dimensional matching, which are classic topics in theoretical computer science. The use of local search algorithms and approximation ratios suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), computational complexity (cs.CC), game theory and economics (cs.GT), or artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
